            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Esta URL de requisição <code>POST</code> nos diz que este novo dado deve ser salvo em <code>courses</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"bash\" name=\"Console Editor\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"POST https://mimo.org/courses\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"21\" endIndex=\"22\" /><option startIndex=\"22\" endIndex=\"29\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>/</code> seguido de <code>courses</code>.</p></body></html>"
